<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Jun1916"><font color="red">4 June 1916</font>, <cite>BLHW</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): I enclose corrections for the third chapter of my novel [A Portrait] so that it may be sent on at once to be set up. Tomorrow I shall send those for the fourth chapter and also the revised cuttings of first and second if they arrive tonight.</div>
